<h2>Update 41G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 17 - FAMILY PAYMENT - Permissable child earning rate for 1994. See guidelines 17.2420 to 17.2421.</p>
<p>1994 rate of weekly permissable child earnings.</p>
<h2>Update 40G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 15 - SPECIAL BENEFIT - Removal of some release pension provisions to chapter 1 and clarification of special benefit provisions. See guidelines 15.3800 to 15.3806.</p>
<p>Enables released prisoners to receive a 'double payment' of special benefit.</p>
<h2>Update 39G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
