<p>This amendment reflects current procedures.</p>
<h2>Update 36G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 1 - GENERAL PROCEDURES inc. TAX FILE NUMBER EXEMPTIONS - Amendment to table of contents to reflect update 37G.</p>
<h2>Update 35G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 27 - DETERMININING RATES OF PAYMENT - Notification of earnings by SPPs. See guidelines 27.8610 to 27.8619.</p>
<p>An OLA text has been created to be used to remind SPPs with earnings to notify promptly of any variation in rate of earnings (OLA Q345).</p>
<h2>Update 34G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 17 - FAMILY PAYMENT - Family payment income and assets test reviews. See guidelines 17.3600 to 17.3603.</p>
<p>This change corrects the guide so that it refers to calculating entitlement to family payment for the current calendar year rather than for the previous calendar year.</p>
<h2>Update 33G # Date 23 September 1993</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 10 - WIDOWED PERSON ALLOWANCE - Clarification of when WPA can be paid. See guidelines 10.000 to 10.1000.</p>
